 shot in the village of Ar'ara on July 29, 2023. As'ad was shot while on his way to work in Ar'ara, driving a small truck he used for his job. HaEmek Hospital announced his death after attempts to save his life were unsuccessful.","review_status":"flagged_for_review","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2023-01-01_2023-12-31","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2023-01-01_2023-12-31","run_id":"canonical","case_index":602}